cars which plunged into the river when a large chunk of the 
twolane roadway fell 25 feet into the river about 845 pm cst 
saturday 
they planned to continue to search until were sure there are 
no other vehicles or victims in there bledsoe said 
the collapse left a 60foot gap in the twolane northbound 
bridge carrying us highway 51 over the hatchie river five miles 
north of here and about 45 miles north of memphis a companion 
